item.title: Benq EH600
item.description: Very bright Full HD projector. 1080p, 3500 lumens, 1.1x Zoom, 1.49~1.64 throw ratio. HDMI and VGA inputs, as well as smart WiFi connectivity. Ideal for gallery installations as well as events.

item.title: NEC P502HL
item.description: Very bright Full HD laser projector. 1080p, 5000 lumens. Lens shift and wide zoom range. Can be supplied with HDBase-T transmitter.

item.title: Panasonic PT-L501U
item.description: SVGA Projector, 1100 lumens. VGA and composite inputs.
